fields.title: Awesome glasses
fields.message: These glasses are amazing. I love how they fit on my face. I wish the color was a little lighter, but other than that I am a very happy customer.
fields.name: David Gandy

fields.title: This is a really nice pair
fields.message: I bought these glasses because a friend loved them. The weight is a little heavy and the temple is a little long but I love the style and how they look. I think for the price these are an excellent buy.
fields.name: Travis Chase

fields.title: Frame color not what I was expecting...
fields.message:
I was really happy with the Warby customer service and speed of
order/delivery, but when I received my glasses, the frames were much
darker than what was shown on the website. Someone should update the
site with a more accurate picture of the Sandalwood Matte. Other than
that, I was happy with the experience.
fields.name: Robert Madole

fields.title: I love my ring!!!
fields.message: This was our first purchase from Gemvara. It was a Mother's Day Present. The ceres ring was a bit smaller than I had pictured, quite dainty. However, the stones are beautiful and shine ever so brightly. It will be an everyday wear. I am pleased with this purchase and will purchase again from Gemvara. Thank you for a great online experience.
fields.name: Kristy Endicott

fields.title: Great, but...
fields.message: I bought 2 of these rings to represent each of my daughters. They are beautiful. I've gotten so many lovely comments on them. However, the rings are thinner than I thought so I'm planning on buying a simple diamond ring to add some "thickness" to the bands. Also I sized my finger between a 5 and 5.5. I bought the 5.5 but I soon discovered that I needed to go a full size down instead!
fields.name: Heather Mitchell

fields.title: Wonderful ring that looks great and she loves it.
fields.message: Extremely pleased. Unlike many jewelry purchased where I always feel the stone is smaller than I thought, this stone met my expectations. The stones were of a nice size and the design complemented the setting very nicely. It looks excellent on my wife and she was delighted with it. Recommended!
fields.name: Jeremy Pratt

fields.title: Gorgeous
fields.message: I always like to pick out something that catches my eye for its style and looks. Anyone can buy what all the other women are wearing and it becomes very dull to see the same look. None of the stores around me had anything like this and that is why it caught my eye for its color and setting. I know my lady will have something that is special and that the other gal's are not wearing.
fields.name: Frank Lee

fields.title: Just Beautiful!
fields.message: From a gem and mineral fanatic these are just perfect! They were a little gift to myself after getting my tax refund for the year and I am so pleased with them. I haven't taken them off since I got them.
fields.name: Jennifer Wilson

fields.title: Gorgeous ring!
fields.message: This ring is absolutely gorgeous. I wanted something more unique than a diamond, and this sapphire fits the bill! My girlfriend, I mean my fiancee (!!), loves it almost as much as she loves me!
fields.name: Dave Gandy

fields.title: Great teacher
fields.message: Peter is a great teacher. When I don't understand something, he's great at figuring out what I'm missing and helping me to understand. Highly recommended.
fields.name: Dave Gandy

fields.title: Peter!
fields.message: I absolutely hate math! I thought I could never understand and had no way of getting through my college math course. I was indeed stressed because I was failing and needed help immediately to bring up my grade. I contacted Peter and I had a two hour session. He was patient, calm, confident and very helpful. In other words he’s awesome! He is a great tutor and is extremely professional. I now have the tools to concur this math course!
fields.name: Princess

fields.title: First-rate
fields.message: Peter is terrific. Truly first-rate. He has a great demeanor and he knows this territory very well. I very much expect a good result from his efforts.
fields.name: Thane R
